<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) No 3567/92 of 10 December 1992 laying down detailed rules for the application of the individual limits, national reserves and transfer of rights provided for in Articles 5a to 5c of Council Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 on the common organization of the market in sheepmeat and goatmeat </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 3567/92, millega kehtestatakse n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 (lamba- ja kitselihaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta) artiklites 5a-5c s&auml;testatud &otilde;iguste &uuml;leandmise, individuaalpiirangute ja riigi varude &uuml;ksikasjalikud rakenduseeskirjad 10. detsember 1992 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 of 25 September 1989 on the common organization of the market in sheepmeat and goatmeat (1), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2069/92 (2), and in particular Articles 5a (4) (b) and (f), 5b (4) and 5c (2) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 25. septembri 1987. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 lamba- ja kitselihaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2069/92, (2) eriti selle artikli 5a l&otilde;ike 4 punkte b ja f, artikli 5b l&otilde;iget 4 ja artikli 5b l&otilde;iget 2, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, with a view to implementing the system of individual limits as introduced by Article 5a of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89, the rules governing the determination of those limits and their communication to the producers should be specified, taking account of the specific problems linked to producer groups and to the different rates of premium in the sheep and goat sector; whereas also certain terms should be defined so as to give effect to the said Article 5a; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: pidades silmas m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikliga 5a kehtestatud individuaalpiirangute s&uuml;steemi rakendamist, tuleks t&auml;psustada nende piirangute m&auml;&auml;ratlemist ja tootjatele teatamist reguleerivad eeskirjad, v&otilde;ttes arvesse tootjar&uuml;hmadega ning lamba- ja kitsesektori erinevate lisatasu m&auml;&auml;radega seotud eriprobleeme; samuti tuleks kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata nimetatud artikli 5a j&otilde;ustumist&auml;htaeg; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, bearing in mind the regulating effect which the system of individual limits will have on the market, provision should be made for premium rights not used by their holder during a specific period to revert to the national reserve; whereas appropriate measures should also be taken to ensure that rights granted free of charge from the national reserve are used by the beneficiaries solely for the intended purposes; </inglise>
<eesti> pidades silmas individuaalpiirangute s&uuml;steemi reguleerivat m&otilde;ju turule, tuleks ette n&auml;ha, et kui lisatasu saamise &otilde;igust teatava aja jooksul ei kasutata, suunatakse see tagasi riigi varudesse; samuti tuleks asjakohaste meetmetega tagada, et lisatasu saajad kasutaksid riigi varudest tasuta saadud &otilde;igusi ainult sihtotstarbeliselt; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the uniform implementation of the provisions relating to the transfer and temporary leasing of rights entails the laying-down of certain administrative rules; whereas, in order to avoid excessive administrative work, the minimum number of rights which may be transferred or temporarily leased should be set at a sufficiently high level, taking into account the special situation of small producers; whereas such rules must also prevent infringement of the obligation under Article 5a (4) of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 to surrender, whenever rights are transferred without transfer of the holding, a certain percentage of such transferred rights to the national reserve; whereas, moreover, provision should be made for this temporary surrender to be limited in time so as to avoid abuse of the transfer rules; </inglise>
<eesti> &otilde;iguste loovutamise ja ajutise &uuml;leandmisega seotud s&auml;tete &uuml;htne rakendamine eeldab teatavate halduseeskirjade kehtestamist; haldusk&uuml;simuste lahendamiseks kuluva aja l&uuml;hendamiseks tuleks n&auml;ha ette piisavalt suur arv loovutatavaid ja ajutiselt &uuml;leantavaid &otilde;igusi, v&otilde;ttes arvesse v&auml;iketootjate erilist olukorda; selliste eeskirjadega tuleb &uuml;htlasi tagada, et ei rikutaks m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikli 5a l&otilde;ikega 4 etten&auml;htud kohustust, mille kohaselt &otilde;iguste loovutamisel ilma talumajapidamise &uuml;leandmiseta tuleb teatav protsent nimetatud &otilde;igustest loovutada riigi varudesse; samuti tuleks ette n&auml;ha &otilde;iguste ajutise &uuml;leandmise aeg, et v&auml;ltida loovutamiseeskirjade rikkumist; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the special case where a producer only uses publicly or collectively owned land for grazing and transfers all his rights to another farmer, thus ceasing production, should be deemed equivalent to the transfer of a holding; </inglise>
<eesti> talumajapidamise &uuml;leandmisega samav&auml;&auml;rseks tuleb pidada erijuhtu, mille puhul tootja kasutab karjakasvatuseks avaliku sektori v&otilde;i kollektiivses omanduses olevat maad ja loovutab tootmist l&otilde;petades k&otilde;ik oma &otilde;igused m&otilde;nele teisele talupidajale; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas application of an administrative system of transfers in which all transfers of rights without transfer of the holding are conducted solely via the national reserve necessitates the establishment of a legal framework designed to preserve economic consistency with the system of direct trasfers between producers; whereas objective criteria should be established for the determination of the sum to be paid by the national reserve to the producer who has transferred his rights and the sum to be paid by the producer who receives equivalent rights from the national reserve; </inglise>
<eesti> kohaldades loovutamise halduss&uuml;steemi, mille puhul k&otilde;ik &otilde;iguste loovutamised ilma talumajapidamise &uuml;leandmiseta toimuvad ainult riigi varude kaudu, on vaja kehtestada &otilde;iguslik raamistik, mis s&auml;ilitaks majandusliku seostatuse s&uuml;steemiga, mille kohaselt toimus &otilde;iguste otsene loovutamine tootjate vahel; tuleks kehtestada objektiivsed kriteeriumid, et m&auml;&auml;rata kindlaks summa, mida riigi varudest peab maksma oma &otilde;igused loovutanud tootjale, ja summa, mida peab maksma riigi varudest samav&auml;&auml;rsed &otilde;igused saanud tootja; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the choice of 1991 as the reference year will cause transitional problems which need to be resolved; whereas, while ensuring that the total number of existing rights is not increased above the number of acquried or potential rights corresponding to 1991 alone, provision should be made for an initial allocation of rights to farmers in well-defined situations; whereas, in order to take account of the exceptional circumstances which preveted producers from applying for a premium for 1992 while having obtained a premium for 1991, provision should be made for such producers to receive rights from the national reserve; whereas, moreover, in conformity with the principle of legitimate expectations, compensation in the form of the allocation of additional rights should be provided for in the case of producers whose individual limit does not reach its normal level because of their participation in a Community extensification programme; </inglise>
<eesti> 1991. aasta valimine v&otilde;rdlusaastaks p&otilde;hjustab &uuml;leminekuprobleeme, mis tuleb lahendada; tagades, et olemasolevate &otilde;iguste koguarv ei ole suurem kui ainult 1991. aastale vastavate saadud v&otilde;i potentsiaalsete &otilde;iguste arv, tuleks ette n&auml;ha &otilde;iguste esialgne andmine selgelt m&auml;&auml;ratletud olukorras olevatele talupidajatele; erandlike asjaolude arvestamiseks, mis takistasid tootjatel taotlemast lisatasu 1992. aastaks, kuigi nad said lisatasu 1991. aasta eest, tuleks s&auml;testada, et sellised tootjad saaksid &otilde;igusi riiklikust varust; samuti tuleks koosk&otilde;las &otilde;igusp&auml;raste ootuste p&otilde;him&otilde;ttega tagada kompensatsioon t&auml;iendavate &otilde;iguste m&auml;&auml;ramise vormis nendele tootjatele, kelle individuaalpiirang ei vasta tavatasemele nende osaluse t&otilde;ttu &uuml;henduse ekstensiivistamisprogrammis; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the Canary Islads have only been subject to the provisions of the common agricultural policy, including the ewe premium arrangements, since 1 July 1992; whereas, therefore, the individual limits for producers located in that territory may not be established by reference to premiums granted for 1991; whereas, in order to stay as close as possible to the economic situation in 1991, the individual limits should be established on the basis and within the limits of the flocks counted in that territory in 1991 while taking into account the premiums granted to producers for 1992; </inglise>
<eesti> Kanaari saarte kohta on &uuml;hise p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitika s&auml;tted, sealhulgas ute kohta makstavate lisatasude m&auml;&auml;ramise kord kehtinud alles alates 1. juulist 1992; seep&auml;rast ei tohi k&otilde;nesoleva territooriumi tootjatele individuaalpiiranguid kehtestada 1991. aastal makstavate lisatasude alusel; s&auml;ilitamaks v&otilde;imalikult suurt sarnasust 1991. aasta majandusolukorraga, tuleks individuaalpiirangud kehtestada k&otilde;nesoleval territooriumil 1991. aastal loendatud karjade &uuml;ldarvu alusel ja piires, v&otilde;ttes arvesse tootjatele 1992. aastal makstud lisatasusid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the transition from the system existing when Regulation (EEC) No 2069/92 entered into force to the system of individual limits may, in certain Member States, cause special problems due to the transfer of premium rights by producers who do not own the land on which their holdings are situated; whereas, in order to ensure the smooth operation of the market, provision should be made for those Member States to take appropriate measures to resolve the problems while respecting the link between producer and premium rights under the system established by Article 5a of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89; </inglise>
<eesti> &uuml;leminek m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2069/92 j&otilde;ustumise ajal kehtinud s&uuml;steemilt individuaalpiirangute s&uuml;steemile v&otilde;ib teatavates liikmesriikides tekitada probleeme, mis on seotud lisatasu saamise &otilde;iguste loovutamisega tootjate poolt, kes ei oma maad, kus nende talumajapidamised asuvad; turu t&otilde;rgeteta toimimiseks peaksid k&otilde;nesolevad liikmesriigid v&otilde;tma nende probleemide lahendamiseks asjakohaseid meetmeid, arvestades m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artiklis 5a kehtestatud s&uuml;steemi alusel tootja seost lisatasu saamise &otilde;igustega; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas if the Commission is to monitor the new arrangements it needs to be properly provided by the Member States with the essential information regarding its implementation; whereas it is therefore vital to require the Member States to communicate the necessary information to the Commission; </inglise>
<eesti> kui komisjon hakkab uut korda j&auml;lgima, peavad liikmesriigid teda n&otilde;uetekohaselt varustama olulise teabega selle rakendamise kohta; seet&otilde;ttu on &auml;&auml;rmiselt oluline n&otilde;uda liikmesriikidelt vajaliku teabe edastamist komisjonile; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the Management Committee for Sheepmeat and Goatmeat has not issued an opinion within the time limit set by its chairman, </inglise>
